You need Arduino IDE, Mincore Installed, USBasp programmer, + dupont jumpers

Pick: ATmega328 (with minicore), an external 16MHz crystal, and USBasp programmer

Take the USBasp programmer and locate the board's ISP headers, and then match the USBasp programmer's pins to the boards and connect them via dunpont jumper wires

Than flash tools-->burn bootloader
sketch --> upload using programmer (only if you change the code)
